The adjusted model confirms the first-pass signals and shows the central heterogeneity: venetoclax/azacitidine is not uniformly beneficial, but has large positive interactions with `unfit_for_intensive` and `npm1_mutation`, and a negative interaction with `tp53_mutation`. I’m checking those strata and a few plausible null interactions before writing the transcript.
